boy pablo.title: boy pablo
boy pablo.description: boy pablo is the indie pop music project of Chilean–Norwegian singer songwriter Nicolas Muñoz.

pocky.title: pocky
pocky.description: pocky is a snack food consisting of chocolate-coated biscuit sticks. It was named after the Japanese onomatopoetic word pokkin.

mangas.title: mangas
mangas.description: mangas are comics or graphic novels originating from Japan. The term manga is used in Japan to refer to both comics and cartooning.
